'''''Galladinium's Galactic Datalog of Fantastic Technology''''', often referred to simply as '''''Galladinium's Datalog''''', was a [[Datalog/Legends|datalog]] purveying fine merchandise to an upscale clientele. Its 50th-anniversary issue was released during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

As many items in the datalog could be used for combat purposes, it was banned by [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Shinda]] of [[Spirva sector/Legends|Spirva Sector]]. As a result, a lucrative smuggling opportunity colloquially known as the "[[Spirva Run]]" developed to deliver items from Galladinium's Datalog into the sector.

==Behind the scenes==
The roleplaying book ''[[Galladinium's Fantastic Technology]]'' maintains the [[in-universe]] conceit that it is the 50th-anniversary issue of ''Galladinium's Datalog''.

